This paper discusses the ethical implications of data technology and the responsibility of researchers and professionals in the field. It also analyzes data ethics codes and their relationship to society and agency. Therefore, the most likely category is cs.CY (Computers and Society), followed by cs.CS (Computer Science and Game Theory), cs.ET (Emerging Technologies), cs.CR (Cryptography and Security), and cs.SI (Social and Information Networks).
